styczynski.weblogic.jdbc.debug.report

Class ExecutionAlert

  • java.lang.Object
    • styczynski.weblogic.jdbc.debug.report.ExecutionAlert

  • public class ExecutionAlert
extends java.lang.Object
    Object used to report execution lasting more that defined threshold. It's used in both log based reporting and in the web based one.
